commit.message:
Add time.sleep() to _read_until (#347)

This should release the Python Gobal Interpreter Lock once per iteration, so the I/O bound paramiko thread get's a chance to run.

commit.message:
Add SSH Agent Forwarding to command execution (#314)

Closes #334

Don't open SFTP connection if scp=ALL was requested (#330)

In the previous implementation all the dictionary values are
evaluated and the one requested is returned. This causes an attempt
to open SFTP connection and an exception if the targer server doesn't
have sftp server which is the case with many embedded system.

Fixed #329
